title: Charlie Ventura & Bill Harris - Live At The Three Deuces (19
description:
CHARLIE VENTURA & BILL HARRIS - LIVE AT THE THREE DEUCES VOL. 1 & 2

CD 1 
1. Characteristically B.H. (B. Harris)
2. Blue Champange (J. Eaton - F. Ryerson - G. Watts)
3. Frolic Sam (C.C. Williams)
4. High On An Open Mike (C. Ventura)
5. Body And Soul (Green - Heyman - Sour)
6. The Great Lie (C. Calloway - A. Gibson)
7. Everything Happens To Me (T. Adair - M. Dennis)

CD 2
1. Eleven Sixty (C. Ventura)
2. All Of Me (G. Marks - S. Simons)
3. The Man I Love (G & I Gershwin)
4. The Happy Monster (G.S. Jackson - W. Bauer)
5. Dark Eyes (P.D.)
7. Broadway (W. Bird - T. McRae - W. Woode)

CD 1 & CD 2 Tracks 1-5:

Charlie Ventura - tenor sax
Bill Harris - trombone
Ralph Burns - piano
Bob Leininger - bass
Curley Russell - bass (CD 1, track 7 & CD 2, track 5)
Dave tough - drums
Teddy Walters - vocal (CD 2, track 2)
Recorded live, 1947

CD 2, track 6:

Bill Harris - trombone
Ray Abrams - tenor sax
Unknown -  piano
Curley Russell - bass
Ed Shaughnessy - drums
Recorded live at Birdland, June, 1952

2000 & 2002 High Note
